28:20.960 --> 28:22.090
saya pergi cari dia.

28:22.350 --> 28:23.920
- Namun dia...
- Jangan namun.

28:23.920 --> 28:24.980
Percayalah cikgu.

28:30.350 --> 28:32.610
Helo, Qin Ao dah larikan diri dari rumah.

28:32.640 --> 28:33.830
Saya tunggu awak di bawah,

28:33.830 --> 28:34.640
kita pergi cari dia bersama-sama.

28:34.640 --> 28:35.350
Baiklah.

28:40.750 --> 28:41.550
Qin Ao.

28:43.110 --> 28:43.920
Qin Ao!

28:49.400 --> 28:50.240
Qin Ao.

28:56.680 --> 28:57.550
Awak dah jumpa diakah?

28:57.550 --> 28:58.790
Belum, saya cari di situ.

28:58.790 --> 28:59.320
